name: Scary Doll Panda - KuD-047
description: He is encased in glass showcase in a bleak looking room. Many says that he is alive, roaming the streets at night searching for something. Yes, he is possessed by lingering soul of blood thrist panda. He is full of hatred and want to get revenge, thats where the stories came from. It's all true, so beware of him when you walking alone in the quite lonely night.
